Swe312-Project Banking System

Banking System project

By: Youmna Jaza
Course: SWE312 Software Constraction & User Interface
Lecturer: Ms. Layla Albabtain

It allows the user to:
  • Creats an account.
  • Sign in using account number and password.
  • Sign in using one time password that's sent to the email associated with the user's account number.
  • Deposit money.
  • Withdraw money.
  • Check balance.
  • Add beneficiaries.
  • Check the added beneficiaries.
  • Check the transactions history.
  • Log out.
Packages 
Package Description
components
Contains the main classes of the project that are related to Database connection and Business Rules.
coordinators
Contains all the coordinators that are associated with GUI and the database.
gui
Contains all the GUI classes.
